description: A lone astronaut floats in space, surrounded by darkness and silence.

dialogue: My ship crashed years ago. I've been adrift ever since.
description: The astronaut looks down at their damaged spaceship, now just a wreckage floating in the void.

dialogue: I can hear something moving around me.
description: Suddenly, the astronaut hears strange noises coming from nearby. They turn around but see nothing.

dialogue: It's getting closer... I can feel its presence.
description: The astronaut feels a chill run down their spine as they realize they are not alone. Something sinister is lurking in the shadows.
